      <p>One feature that really stuck out was a counter-pick option only on LeagueDroid. When selected, it brings up an easily accessible menu of champions that counter other champions. For example, if you are having issues with Garen, you could see that he is weak against Teemo and Yorick but strong against Riven and Jax. This can help bring you an even greater advantage during those tough nights of ranked solo-queue.</p>
